PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778746040
OL,3,CFive teenagers sentenced after
OL,4,Cfriend's death in car crash
OL,6,FTwo of the boys fled while both girls
OL,7,Fand the driver remained at the site of
OL,8,Fthe crash.
OL,10,FA helicopter and search teams were
OL,11,Fdeployed to find them, after which all
OL,12,Ffive were treated for minor injuries
OL,13,Fand were arrested.
OL,15,FThe driver of the vehicle, a 16-year-
OL,16,Fold boy who cannot be named because of
OL,17,Fhis age, was sentenced to four years
OL,18,Fin custody after appearing at Bradford
OL,19,FCrown Court on Monday.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778746040
OL,3,CFive teenagers sentenced after
OL,4,Cfriend's death in car crash
OL,6,FHe was also disqualified from driving
OL,7,Ffor seven years and must pass an
OL,8,Fextended driving test.
OL,10,FThe four other teenagers were
OL,11,Fsentenced at Bradford Youth Court on
OL,12,F20 April.
OL,14,FThe 16-year-old girl who initially
OL,15,Ftook the vehicle admitted to
OL,16,Faggravated vehicle taking.
OL,18,FThe girl, a 15-year-old boy, 18-year-
OL,19,Fold boy and 16-year-old girl, also
OL,20,Fadmitted the offence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
